headline: S&P Global Mobility projects moderate U.S. auto sales for June 2025 at 1.27 million units
summary: S&P Global Mobility projects new light vehicle sales volume in June 2025 will reach 1.27 million units. With only 24 selling days for the month, unadjusted volume comparisons would be down compared to June 2024 (26 selling days) and the month-prior (27 selling days in May 2025), absent other impacts.
